additional_info:
Example, to hide the dice roller and help button, you would remove all code blocks but these:

#diceroller {
  display: none !important;
}
#helpsite {
  display: none !important;
}

css:
/*macro quickbar */
@-moz-document domain("app.roll20.net") {
#select {
  display: none !important;
}
#editinglayer {
  display: none !important;
}
#drawingtools {
  display: none !important;
}
#fxtools {
  display: none !important;
}
#zoompanel {
  display: none !important;
}
#measure {
  display: none !important;
}
#fogcontrols {
  display: none !important;
}
#startrounds {
  display: none !important;
}
#diceroller {
  display: none !important;
}
#helpsite {
  display: none !important;
}
}
